            "position": "right",
            "distance": "far",
            "voice": "",
            "id": "line_2"
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "盗窃犯",
            "text": "唯一的线索还是与C息息相关宗教项链，我只能认为房间是你精心布置后的样子",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right",
            "distance": "far",
            "voice": "",
            "id": "line_4"
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "老囚",
            "text": "说起来之前都是你在指认啊。不知不觉陷入你的话术里去了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right",
            "distance": "far",
            "voice": "",
            "id": "line_6"
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
